      "content": "i hear what you're saying about hope, but i just don't feel it. everything feels fundamentally broken. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to find a reason to keep going when the biggest reason for my happiness is just... gone. it feels like the only way to actually find peace and stop this weight is to just not have to deal with the mornings anymore. does that make sense?",
